* Error Handling\nStrategies
** Drop Invalid Records
***_ expect_or_drop in pipelines
***_ Filter missing required columns
***_ Tracks drop metrics
** Fail on Critical Violations
***_ ON VIOLATION FAIL UPDATE
***_ Stops pipeline immediately
***_ Prevents bad data propagation
***_ For structural integrity issues
** Quarantine Pattern
***_ Route bad records to separate table
***_ Valid records continue to silver
***_ Invalid records to quarantine table
***_ Investigate without blocking flow
** Benefits
***_ Data quality enforced
***_ No silent failures
***_ Auditable error records
***_ Operational flexibility
@endmindmap
